{"tid":867762,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 痛擊系四人大亂鬥。Blade-smash ブレイドスマッシュ  處女爭奪戰2","createTime":"2018-10-19T02:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T02:17:58.000Z","uid":9526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5b298899373abbb41326ef15a5404e45ab284cf1","tid":867762,"uid":9526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d7g8ljXGcNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd7g8ljXGcNc&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=74564a46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d7g8ljXGcNc</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OAUDmpXU0GQ/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FOAUDmpXU0GQ%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=5c94c252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://www.blade-smash.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blade-smash.jp%2F&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2cffc07e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.blade-smash.jp/</a><br />\nIOS(日版): <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1345281878?l=ja&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1345281878%3Fl%3Dja%26ls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4d1663da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1345281878?l=ja&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\nAN: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.gu3.ninjaka\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.co.gu3.ninjaka&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ea040198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.gu3.ninjaka</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(AN機建議用QOOAPP下載)</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBlade-Smash ブレイドスマッシュ<br />\n<br />\n簡介: 痛擊系PVP橫向格鬥game, 有四人大混戰, 爽快打擊感, 技能特效強<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Q&amp;A:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1) 最緊係, 老老豆豆駛唔駛刷首抽先?</strong></span></span><br />\n隻GAME一開始會送四星必中, 四隻都好強, 夠玩到你11抽<br />\n我個人唔建議刷首抽, 因為呢隻GAME四星好強某部份四星係「好用」過五星<br />\n所謂「好用」指技能, 之後再談<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2)四星打唔打得贏五星?</strong></span></span><br />\n打得贏, 首先隻GAME克屬已經扣好多, 痛擊特效會強好多, 如果無克屬/比人克屬打中左人個硬直無咁強, 好易比人走甩一套連普攻 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3)咩叫連普攻? 有咩攻擊技巧?</strong></span></span><br />\n攻擊有好多樣性, 第一普通連技啦 如果克屬打人例如火打風, 對方個硬直會比較高, 好易就連到全套技<br />\n<br />\n第二就有兩招普通技能, 每隻英雄都唔同的, 有啲三星可能會好相似, 四星五星技能組都幾特別暫時我未見過完全一樣既技能, 相信係唔會有的, 而四星/三星角色有機會技能組好用過五星<br />\n<br />\n最後就係大技, 初頭玩唔係好覺, 點解成日儲唔到大技, 係因為大技條BAR係同閃移係同一條BAR黎 如果成日比人打飛 你要靠閃移番場入面 係永遠都出唔到大技 所以如果你不停打到對手飛出場外, 佢要KEEP住用閃移番黎 佢會出唔到大技<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4)有冇咩特別操作?</span></span></strong><br />\n跳有二段跳, 唔夠跳就可以用閃移: 方向+攻擊 9撳一定用到<br />\n空中可以斬人, 空中都可以向下斬<br />\n另外最實用係兩隻手指撳實MON 佢就會進行格檔 注意番佢都係用大技條BAR 你撳實佢會扣氣扣得好快 扣哂就爆盾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5)武器類型?屬性?</span></strong></span><br />\n武器有手裡劍(忍具), 劍(有斧外型都係劍), 鎚, 拳, 杖(法師)<br />\n屬性火&gt;風&gt;水, 光&gt;暗&gt;克三屬, 三屬&gt;無屬&gt;光暗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>6)有冇咩角色係推薦</strong></span></span><br />\n暫時未試哂, 但有小小心得<br />\n五星推薦暗劍 暗鎚 水鎚(改弱左但都仲屈緊要配4星水劍) <br />\n四星推薦無屬爆炸糖劍女 水拳女, 水劍男, (次一級:火NIGGER 火獅子)<br />\n三星推薦 風結他ROCK友(一招大技秒全世界)<br />\n<br />\n呢個版本暗劍FOR SURE!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">7)限界突破點做?有咩用?</span></strong></span><br />\n基礎能力提升, 點做就係抽到重複既角色佢自動會變成限界突破材料<br />\n三星會變三星材料, 四星會變四星 武器同角色既限界突破材料係可以混用既<br />\n所以隻GAME算係好易就限界突破到 唔駛話你想升某隻角色, 就一定要指定重複佢先可以升到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8)點抽角色?</span></strong></span><br />\n抽角色/抽武器可以用三種唔同方法: 一用忍石, 二用(有償)忍石, 三用GACHA券<br />\n1)忍石入手方法只有好少, 暫時我知就係做佢既任務,例如初心者開局邀朋友玩 每次25粒 做5次<br />\n2)有償忍石姐係課金先有<br />\n3)GACHA券就係做好多任務拎到, 你當係普通GAME既石就得, 佢儲滿條BAR(100) 就會比一張券你, 一張券就一抽, 10張券就11抽送多1抽<br />\n**注意回體一定要用忍石 唔可以用GACHA券<br />\n<br />\nBTW開左個LIHKG公會 名: <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Lihkg</span></strong></span><br />\n同埋新AC要係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>72小時內</ins></strong></span></span>做哂初心者邀人開房任拎5*25粒忍石呀!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\nTemplate :<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fvF9ruXqvGY7MYGQPjP4Uf65ekxph37U9bXFEZiA1tY/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1fvF9ruXqvGY7MYGQPjP4Uf65ekxph37U9bXFEZiA1tY%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d2aa4229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fvF9ruXqvGY7MYGQPjP4Uf65ekxph37U9bXFEZiA1tY/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後, 未隻抽過既帳號頭10個會送一抽, 之後每一個加20GACHA卷 <br />\n快啲黎入TG+入公會隻抽啦: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Djb2ug2SWgcj6y_DjgkUGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDjb2ug2SWgcj6y_DjgkUGg&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f4e793e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Djb2ug2SWgcj6y_DjgkUGg</a>"},{"pid":"0e7fe3c66dc25cfcd011c42179516ac5473edf1f","tid":867762,"uid":90226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"仲未維護完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d0c3a574a04e8b624100e2e5cfa37294adae85","tid":867762,"uid":51728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T03:39:51.000Z